   MEDITATION-SPACES (Undated) _ ``You don't need a separate room
for meditation,'' Diane von Furstenberg said recently. ``I meditate
every morning in my bed for a half hour before I get up.'' Still,
when the designer moved her showroom and offices to an enormous
carriage house in the West Village last year, one space became her
yoga room. Ms. Von Furstenberg is one of many people of means who
has recently dedicated a room to pursue meditation. By Bob Morris.
