sick,' `` she said.
</P>
<P>
   Sandee Sykes, the president of the Woods of Brushy Creek
Neighborhood Association, said she had not heard of such widespread
illness from her neighbors.
</P>
<P>
   Sykes, who went door to door to make sure her neighbors had all
the information they needed, said, ``People aren't dropping like
flies, but they should be concerned.''
</P>
