   WAR-MEMORIES _ The movie ``Saving Private Ryan'' is reviving
memories of World War Two for many older Georgians and Southerners,
especially those who experienced D-Day and, on the home front, were
among the unfortunate who received news in the mail of a loved
one's death. An emotional look back with several who lived through
it. (Hendrick, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
