   WITH
</P>
<P>
   ALZHEIMERS-SIDE _ About 4 million Americans have Alzheimer's
disease. One in 10 people age 65 or older _ and nearly half of
those age 85 or older _ have Alzheimer's. Seven out of 10 people
with Alzheimer's disease live at home. (And other Alzheimer's
facts.) (Fuchs, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
