   REYNOLDS _ DAYTON, Ohio _Dayton-based Reynolds &AMP; Reynolds lands
a $200 million, five-year services contract with Kaiser Permanente,
the largest not-for-profit health maintenance organization in the
U.S. Perhaps this good news will boost Reynolds' stock price, which
has stubbornly refused to climb despite good news from the company.
(Drummond, Dayton Daily News) ETA: 8 p.m.
</P>
