   FALCONS _ Shane Dronett has moved from a career reserve role to
starter at right defensive tackle. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 13-15.
</P>
<P>
   FALCONS-NEWS _ Training camp news story. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 10-12.
