<P>
   SEC-FOOTBALL _ BIRMINGHAM _ As Florida and Tennessee highlight
the final day of the SEC football media days, one question will
likely arise _ is this the year that Tennessee beats Florida?
Despite winning the SEC championship last season, Tennessee lost to
Florida for the fifth straight year. The Vols host the Gators Sept.
19 in Knoxville. (Barnhart, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
