Michigan girl seeking an abortion in Wichita, Kan., isn't as rare
as many might think.
</P>
<P>
   Thousands of young girls nationwide are getting abortions. Last
year, 48 Kansas girls ages 14 and under underwent the procedure, as
did 121 Missouri girls, in their respective states. By Judy L.
Thomas. Story will move in the ``a'' category.
