<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   PROBE-DILEMMA (Washington) -- President Clinton is now left with
just two options: Repeat his denial of a sexual relationship with
Monica Lewinsky to the grand jury, or admit to an affair and, in
effect, confess to the federal crime of perjury. By Brian McGrory.
1400 words.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
