SITCOMS-TVCOLUMN (Pasadena, Calif.) - The legacy of Seinfeld is the
pursuit of nothingness. Accordingly, a comedy sameness has come
over the big networks, and grown-up comedy makers have begun to
turn elsewhere for distribution. In the next few weeks, two cable
