<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-30 20:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1264 &Cx1f; tta-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-POWERBALL-525&AMP;ADD-NYT     07-30 1073
