<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-30 20:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1281 &Cx1f; tab-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MAPLELEAF-HOLLYWOOD-I     07-30 1211
