<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-30 21:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1325 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ALLEN-CHARTER-NYT &LR;      07-30 0732
</HEADER>
