in Santa Barbara. The new owners, who bought the ranch April 21,
want to eventually give visitors unprecedented access to the ranch,
to offer insights about Reagan's lifestyle. So far, they have
invited a few reporters to take a peek. (Steve Malone/Santa Barbara
News-Press Photo)
